name: treading water #1
description:
water can have many shapes and forms, it shifts and shuffles in any conceivable way.
true nfts are unique interations of the same thing, repeating and at the same time changing. water truly permutates, it generates truly unique structures, folds into itself and spreads all over our world. this is the natural beauty of water, it is the structure that our existence is weaved into. i do not provide mere pictures, i provide unique moments, experiences frozen in time, nfts that are made by natures procedurally generated beauty.
